[{"id":"Ugwl8-rE87eUb2_3eYh4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"The quest of kings!","like_count":0,"author_id":"UC8GD13Ktk5xvUgv8BXvb0Sw","author":"@SirMexicanYCP","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_nLUEI0KV4yiOX9-vI3I7P5ccIUEA_i-3YAop3fKsNH7Q=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@SirMexicanYCP","is_favorited":false,"_time_text":"8 months ago","timestamp":1756425600,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"Ugy44GDZLMYB5qTqYNF4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"I was hoping that at the end would be one line Yoshi note 😀","like_count":0,"author_id":"UC-v5h7dDAg5YbRf4mG8iHFw","author":"@Abelhawk","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_leODaL__mpjMH-Snc4YKVY0RO2cOVlzdWt1s8HLvVNEgQ=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@Abelhawk","is_favorited":false,"_time_text":"3 years ago","timestamp":1682726400,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgzWpz75wt9R2IpEdEB4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"Graham death Qoutes\n\nThat old witch caught Graham Todally off guard\nIt looks like Graham will be hanging around here for awhile \nWell Graham, how does it feel to be a pop-sickle \nPoor Graham, it’s a dog eat dog world out there\nWhat an ambomible situation Graham has found himself in \nUh oh, that last step was a doozy \nHate to harp on the subject, but Graham was no match for the vicious harpies\nToo bad, it looks like the eyes have it. \n\nThat wasn’t wise Graham, he who speaks with forked tongue should never be trusted\nThat wasn’t a smart move Graham, bee seeing you\nTisk Tisk, Graham should know better than to feed the bears. \nToo bad, even the sting of such a small creature can prove deadly\nDying for a drink Graham? \nCheer up Graham, at least you can practice your game of Tiddlywinks \nGraham should know better than to keep things bottled up inside.","like_count":0,"author_id":"UC6vT-ho5v-EILM_fQBtqnFA","author":"@Yourpetcatagain","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_mRxxxsKOb33xpNQ9ot_oH8PUz9JvNJlOBw4ofTyhfmlEVL=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@Yourpetcatagain","is_favorited":false,"_time_text":"3 years ago","timestamp":1682726400,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgyOKtH7BCXga2yt1-x4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"As the sky rain blood and the angels cry,\nSeconds seem like years as I wait to die.\nAs I'm surrounded by madness, fear and dread,\nThis is the sound that runs though my head.","like_count":0,"author_id":"UCLujvtvJJcUXn3cc_8_H1HQ","author":"@Algahiem","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_k9-De_aDBNKhORVeiigx3u1Hy64fb2gRCjgPRoqVA=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@Algahiem","is_favorited":false,"_time_text":"12 years ago","timestamp":1398729600,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgyW0i-o3YU9nGPgUAt4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"I had to turn my speakers up for this.","like_count":0,"author_id":"UC5ZC2jRG1ncVSudZi13ZdTQ","author":"@TheMysteryMuffinMan","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_m55SvnyeIqxPXlXmdgduPEpiHkgIFIOt57HFw47WU=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@TheMysteryMuffinMan","is_favorited":false,"_time_text":"13 years ago","timestamp":1367193600,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"Ugwg3G99RCPSnlZeGU94AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"Hah. Hahaha... ","like_count":0,"author_id":"UCJ0v_KaJpheS4o8I0u7IGzw","author":"@LoloGuru","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_nf4_NHC7ETcaFhFjE-yGgdSA-6HVdYbFLciH0iMePH3A=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@LoloGuru","is_favorited":false,"_time_text":"13 years ago","timestamp":1367193600,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgzzlBQXVpvGBCpq58h4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"I often do that with MPC, but here's a funny story: I did it in this case because the entire original track is composed on a SINGLE MIDI CHANNEL. The bass notes, the chords, and the melody are all done on one track, using one instrument, while the other tracks are relegated to the ambient 'sound effects'. I was having trouble picking the melody out of the chords, and ended up experimenting until I got the less chaotic-sounding version.\n\nOne million dollar budget.","like_count":3,"author_id":"UCuSVSeiwAeCg_z6Dn7-cPpQ","author":"@MediaMunkee","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_ncYbSdSA9uPB_8WZdLESAE3cKNZsG94vToV-6BFN6rOmE=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":true,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@MediaMunkee","is_favorited":false,"_time_text":"14 years ago","timestamp":1335657600,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgzZf4vC8vso1BUArH54AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"Wait- KQ5 The Town 2 v2? As in you made a different second part, listened to it, thought \"no, it was more annoying than that\" then willingly made an ADDITIONAL track of this shit that was more along the lines of the original shit? Above and beyond doesn't even begin to cover this.","like_count":1,"author_id":"UC_VzgdjmBEBlbAMKpnl5N1Q","author":"@JorealConners","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_kQ6EoZbJ8k2WsqcKbXtrleFQoU-1Poho4UQvENaGE=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@JorealConners","is_favorited":false,"_time_text":"14 years ago","timestamp":1335657600,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"Ugz3CjwHgDbiAZGTxRh4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"Distortion Guitar is the best bass","like_count":0,"author_id":"UCccj6p0yTwv-wUuZrtrLGNg","author":"@jorbizzle","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/x4jm9mIKNBo-c2_ZXvvAKuPohY-JEqc0ptLYvmCLXzqV-LnnalzNlMggwG7SkBh9OLadXR0qaQ=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_is_verified":false,"author_url